      "description": "Self-contained workspace with tab-based panels: closing a panel's last tab collapses the panel; closing all panels reveals a configurable fallback. Exposes useWorkspace context and a WorkspaceHandle ref for programmatic control. Bundles its internal tab strip and drag context.",
